<plot>Danny, a senior year law school student, can't afford his last semester's tuition. Taking some bad advice from his shady mentor Jerry, he fakes a slip and fall accident to get insurance money to pay his tuition. After going to a loan shark to get him the tuition money up front and some help from an assembly line of crooked lawyers, doctors, and chiropractors, his insurance claim is called into question and challenged by his law school's smug and arrogant dean. In order to make it through his senior year and repay the loan shark he must now defend his claim. His not-so-innocent slip &amp; fall becomes a matter of survival.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?501668</url></doc>
